<title type="html"><![CDATA[12/3 (Thu.) Year-end reflection / Action figure collection (Host: Lawrence)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=450&amp;p=468#p468"><![CDATA[
<span style="color: #FF0000">Place:</span> 丹堤咖啡, 台北市延平南路107號2樓 (MRT 西門站4號出口)<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000"><span style="text-decoration: underline">Agenda:</span></span><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">6:30</span>-7:15 pm Free talk<br />7:15-7:50 pm Session 1 discussion<br />7:50-8:15 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited, 2 mins / each member)<br />8:15-8:45 pm Session 2 discussion<br />8:45-<span style="color: #FF0000">9:00</span> pm Presentation<br /><br />Session 1: Year-end reflection<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://gavinedley.com/december-a-month-for-reflection/">https://gavinedley.com/december-a-month-for-reflection/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.In 2020, did you experience any change in your life? Bad and good?<br />2.This year, is there anyone you are so thankful to or for what?<br />3.What do you think you would like to make anew or let go of this year? Family, relationship, career, time or money management, spiritual life, health ----?<br />4.What did you learn the most this year in our club?<br />5.What do you think you can do to improve your English speaking?<br /><br />---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session 2: Action figure collection<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://geektoyscollectibles.com/%EF%BB%BF6-benefits-of-toy-collecting/">http://geektoyscollectibles.com/%EF%BB% ... ollecting/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Do you agree with the author’s opinion in the article about toy collection or action figure?<br />2.Do you collect any action figure? Why? Why not?<br />3.Do you know any story about collecting things, your friends? Social celebrity?<br />4.If you want to collect an action figure, what would you like to collect? Why?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=25437">Michael</a> — Sun Nov 29, 2020 10:17 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
